# The CFO‚Äôs Guide to Fixing Cash Flow Gaps  
_By Arron Bennett ‚Ä¢ Strategic CFO ‚Ä¢ Founder, Bennett Financials_  
üìÖ **September 9, 2025**  

> [üîó Read this article on BennettFinancials.com](https://bennettfinancials.com/the-cfos-guide-to-fixing-cash-flow-gaps/)

